data.description: Don't miss your chance to own this home in wonderful Neely Manor. Great price for all this square footage! Priced below tax appraisal. This spacious 2 story has an open concept with stylish & sensible living space. Features include a formal living room, and dining room. Inviting fireside family room that overlooks the large eat-in kitchen. Second level offers generously sized bedrooms throughout. Walk-in closets. Laundry room. Relax and enjoy your morning coffee from your covered front porch just waiting for some rocking chairs. Great community is centrally located between Historic Covington/Conyers. Shopping, interstate, and dining are all within minutes.
